# PromptInc 🤖 — Free AI Startup Simulator

[![Play Now](https://img.shields.io/badge/▶️_Play_Now-promptinc.app-blue?style=for-the-badge)](https://promptinc.app)
[![GitHub stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/suchenyang0910-glitch/promptinc?style=flat-square)](https://github.com/suchenyang0910-glitch/promptinc)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

**Build your own AI startup empire** in this free browser-based incremental/idle game. Click to launch, hire AI workers, upgrade GPU servers, and scale from a garage startup to a global AI company.

▶️ **Play now: [promptinc.app](https://promptinc.app)** — no download, no ads, no signup required.

---

## 🎮 Gameplay

| Stage | What You Do |
|-------|------------|
| **1. Click to Build** | Click the launch button to earn initial valuation |
| **2. Hire AI Workers** | Spend valuation to hire automated income generators |
| **3. Upgrade Servers** | Unlock GPU clusters for exponential growth multipliers |
| **4. Scale Empire** | Deploy AI agents, unlock new products, dominate the market |

### Idle Mechanics
- Passive income accrues even when you're away
- Prestige-like reset mechanics for deeper progression
- Multiple upgrade paths: workers, servers, R&D, marketing

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ **Free to play** — no download, no ads, no microtransactions
- ✅ **Browser-native** — works on desktop and mobile
- ✅ **Idle income system** — earn while AFK
- ✅ **7+ AI worker types** — from junior devs to agent swarms
- ✅ **GPU server upgrades** — exponential growth curve
- ✅ **Pure simulation** — no real money, no gambling, no NFTs

