## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Framework | Next.js (App Router) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS |
| Database | Supabase (PostgreSQL) |
| Deployment | Cloudflare / Vercel |
| Analytics | Google Analytics (G-*) |

---

## 🚀 Getting Started (Development)

```bash
git clone git@github.com:suchenyang0910-glitch/promptinc.git
cd promptinc
pnpm install
pnpm dev
```

Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) to see the game.

---

## 📐 Project Structure

```
├── app/            # Next.js App Router pages
├── components/     # Reusable UI components
├── games/          # Game logic modules
├── lib/            # Utility functions
├── content/        # SEO content (guides, FAQs)
├── public/         # Static assets
├── supabase/       # Database migrations
└── scripts/        # Build & content generation tools
```

